DM help files currently available:
	pflags --list current player flags
	oflags --list current object flags
	rflags --list current room flags
	mflags --list current monster flags
	xflags --list current exits flags
	sflags --list current spell flags
	otypes --list object types
	oset ----list *set commands for objects
	pset ----list *set commands for players
	scrolls -list scrolls
	wear ----list wear locations
	titles --list class titles
	char ----list character classes and races
	realms --list realms and proficiencies 
	exp -----list the experience points table
	star ----list the DM *commands
	quest ---list the quest objects
	pers ----list personalized items
	pot -----list potions
